Introduction

AMPERS&ONE is a seven-member boy group under FNC Entertainment. They made their debut on November 15, 2023, with the single album "Ampersand One".

The name of their group is "AMPERS&ONE". It is a combination of two words - "Ampersand" which means '&', and "ONE" which represents unity. The name signifies that we, as individuals, come together as one to achieve our dreams and goals.

The fandom name is "ANDEAR," a combination of "AND" linking AMPERS&ONE and its fans, and "DEAR" connoting beloved and precious, symbolizing the precious connection between AMPERS&ONE and the fans.
